name: Q.E.D.
description: Quod Erat Digitandum. A sophisticated transcription engine for the mathematically gifted but penmanship-challenged. We transform your chaotic scribbles into pristine, WCAG 2.2 AA compliant HTML—because while your proofs are rigorous, your handwriting shouldn’t be a test of faith. From rendering flawless n-dimensional manifolds to turning your "artistic" sketches into diagrams that actually obey the laws of physics, we ensure your work is accessible to everyone. Even those who can’t read "Crayola-on-Napkin."
